{"id":276432,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/美国之音-香港议员梁国雄入境澳门赴婚宴被拒入/","date":"2013-01-27T06:01:20Z","modified":"2013-01-27T06:01:20Z","title":"美国之音 | 香港议员梁国雄入境澳门赴婚宴被拒入境","content":"<p><div><span>香港 <span>—</span></span></p>\n<p><span>香港泛民主派立法会议员、绰号“长毛”的梁国雄星期六以个人身份，前往澳门参加一位友人的婚宴，被澳门当局拒绝入境，被迫返回香港。</span></p>\n<p><span>梁国雄1月26日下午乘船抵达澳门，过关时被扣留在一房间内，尽管他出示律师朋友的婚宴请柬，但仍以他对澳门“内部报案的稳定构成威胁”为由被拒绝入境。</span></p>\n<p><span>梁国雄向媒体抨击澳门当局打压，过分紧张，连不涉及政治的私人活动也不准许，做法野蛮无理。</span></p>\n<p><span>梁国雄曾到澳门参与基本法23条的咨询活动，2007年也曾入境澳门声援当时的五一劳动节活动，此后被几次拒绝入境。</span></p>\n</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://fullrss.net/v/b5751a1dab57f57671c5d503ab58280b/http://www.voachinese.com/content/hongkong-macau-20130127/1591659.html\" border=\"0\" /></div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/\">fullrss.net</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dFc0V1d0REQ4RkJ5d25uWFowVTNhWUE6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"328\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代 </a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":998,"categories":[18270,18269,8779],"tags":[19814,18620,10110,12012,8712]}